Hi friends =F0=9F=91=8B,=C2=A0
Sometimes I write about topics that I think are so important that I get wor=
ried I won=E2=80=99t do them justice. I worry that since I=E2=80=99ve gotte=
n things wrong or gotten overly excited in the past, I won=E2=80=99t have a=
s much gravitas as I need to throw behind the topic. I worry that I=E2=80=
=99m not quite good enough to fit the puzzle together in the way it deserve=
s. Today is one of those topics.=C2=A0=C2=A0
Regenerative finance (ReFi) is one of those radical ideas that are easy to =
dismiss as overly idealistic until it worms itself into your brain and you =
begin to wonder things like, =E2=80=9CWell, why not?=E2=80=9D and =E2=80=9C=
Wouldn=E2=80=99t it actually make a lot more sense to do it this way?=E2=80=
=9D=C2=A0
If you didn=E2=80=99t do anything for Earth Day on Friday =E2=80=94 no judg=
ment =E2=80=94 then take the time to read this piece and think about ways y=
ou might contribute.
Today is a sponsored deep dive on Celo (more on the process here [ https://=
email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkU1vhCAQhn-NHA2grHrg0GS7aXa7vTTZtCeDMCpZBctHN_=
774npoAjMTJjPvmwcpAgzWrXyxPqAttGFdgBt4-AlCAIeiB9dqxcmB1gUrG6R4qUjNaqR92zuAW=
eiJBxcBLbGbtBRBW_OcwJgyNPKqZxWWVU_6A6F9ShQKSXFZgqgEbppdV0SlwUjg8AtutQbQxMcQ=
Fp8VLxk9paOs9Plg7TBBLu28v8QZTNjKdMmFlurlwu7V-1v8vvrzdVVUyOPnz6PuXtV5bhepb26=
-fXxtK0HpkBWn6JesOPpROG0GpDnFNJmjjFBWY5wXeXkQpOsFafquroSQWYnngeY-dj4Ied-8IM=
eNDZ3dVqT2fRQzTM9GYtKmPEejw9qCEd0EascVdupPgO0ABlz6DdWKkFgzXDckBUwOO57Ek9GKV=
skcSsrKpinzL_oHwd-Zng ]) =E2=80=93 and if you=E2=80=99re building a ReFi pr=
oject, I hope this gets you to take a look at Celo =E2=80=93 but the more i=
mportant mission here is to explain ReFi in a way that makes sense and gets=
 you excited enough to build, invest in, or otherwise support a ReFi projec=
