n, then architecture.&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px;=
 line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">But mission-first doesn&#8217;t mea=
n technically simple. Quite the opposite: it means <strong>doing really har=
