herefore more environmentally friendly, than Proof-of-Work. <strong>Blockch=
ains don&#8217;t need to be environmentally harmful.</strong> Today, <stron=
g>Celo is carbon-negative</strong> thanks to its automatic purchase of offs=
ets through <a href=3D"https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkc2OpSAQhZ9Gdhp=
