e=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;=
">The things that most users in Celo&#8217;s network care about are being a=
ble to send, receive, and access money from their phones, off-ramp easily, =
do things that have the potential to earn money, and pay low fees.&nbsp;</p=
><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 =
0 1em 0;">That&#8217;s where things like the <strong>mobile-first experienc=
