yle=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em =
0;">Celo, and the ReFi movement, might provide the tools to level the playi=
ng field by connecting the interests and contributions of people around the=
 globe, and by backing a new money with the things we want to see more of i=
n the world.&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-hei=
ght: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">Money is just a technology, and today, peopl=
